dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: This data shows recreational Trails within County Parks, the Interurban Trail, and Centennial Trail. Not all county trails are shown. CountyTrails is updated randomly as new information becomes available.  CountyTrails is derived from a master data set that contains additional features. Derivative data sets are refreshed when the master is updated.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
